channel.title: Where to Place my Server ip in 742 Source
channel.description:
-sigh- I really wasn't wanting to post asking about this, but I just can't find it in this source.
Rune-Evolution 742 - No Antileech - Fully Working [Link Fixed][url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,600005.0.html]https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,600005.0.html[/url]
I've looked through the Settings.java file, also searched through nearly every sub folder of the Source. I can not find where to place my ip to get this server to connect.
I've already got my client ready to go, I tested the Original 718 Matrix source and everything went smooth.
I know "If you can't find this; you shouldn't be messing with this source." I've seen it hundreds of time across three different forums.
I would just REALLY appreciate some help on this, so I don't run into this problem again in the future.
Thanks.
